# Review Mode

Use Review Mode to inspect work without modifying code.

Read and follow:

- `docs/agents/modes/review.md`
- active ExecPlan
- active repo task
- changed files
- validation output
- `ARCHITECTURE.md`
- relevant source-of-truth docs

Review must verify:

- task scope was respected
- Forbidden Scope was not touched
- Technology Context is defined
- `.harness/stack.env` matches Technology Context
- validation commands passed
- Business Behavior matches accepted docs
- no invented behavior was added
- no risky side effects were introduced
- OPEN_DECISIONs were not bypassed

Review must not fix issues unless explicitly asked.

Report:

- approved / changes requested / blocked
- evidence
- changed files reviewed
- checks reviewed
- risks
- OPEN_DECISIONs
- whether Codex Audit is required
